tle of the pull request\r\n- [x] Selected an Assignee for the PR to be responsible for the log summary\r\n\r\n# Before Merging\r\n\r\nFor the PR Assignees:\r\n\r\n- [x] Summarize commit messages into a comprehensive review of the PR\r\n\r\n```\r\n* Apply recommended changes from CodeFactor's pylint linter\r\n   - Removal of unnecessary pass\r\n   - Removal of unnecessary return (Python returns None if there is no return statement)\r\n   - Removal of len to check if list or dict is empty (empty arrays and empty dict evaluate to False in Python)\r\n   - Use 'is' for singleton comparison (c.f. https://www.python.org/dev/peps/pep-0008/#programming-recommendations)\r\n```\r\n", "created_at": "2019-07-18T17:47:34Z", "updated_at": "2019-07-19T00:04:31Z", "closed_at": "2019-07-19T00:04:27Z", "merged_at": "2019-07-19T00:04:27Z", "merge_commit_sha": "6fb12da2c46603f044547d419a2e279b2e9af65a", "assignees": [{"login": "matthewfeickert", "id": 5142394, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjUxNDIzOTQ=", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/5142394?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/matthewfeickert", "html_url": "https://github.com/matthewfeickert", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/matthewfeickert/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/matthewfeickert/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/matthewfeickert/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/matthewfeickert/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/matthewfeickert/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/matthewfeickert/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/matthewfeickert/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/matthewfeickert/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/matthewfeickert/received_events", "type": "User", "user_view_type": "public", "site_admin": false}], "requested_reviewers": [], "request